### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### INGESTION  (skip if already seeded via seed_vehicles.http)
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### ── 2. Ingest Tesla Model 3
POST http://localhost:8080/vehicles/ingest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": "tesla-model3-2025-long-range",
  "year": 2025,
  "make": "Tesla",
  "model": "Model 3",
  "trim": "Long Range",
  "bodyStyle": "Sedan",
  "engine": "Dual motor electric",
  "horsepower": 450,
  "torque": 471,
  "drivetrain": "AWD",
  "transmission": "Single-speed automatic",
  "mpgCity": "134",
  "mpgHighway": "126",
  "msrp": "$47,990",
  "features": ["panoramic glass roof", "adaptive cruise control", "heated seats", "autopilot"],
  "summary": "Long-range electric sedan with 450hp dual motors and advanced Autopilot."
}

