### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### SINGLE-VEHICLE ASK  — POST /vehicles/{vehicleId}/ask
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### ── 4. Ask about Tesla specs (HYBRID mode — default)
### Expected: LLM answer with horsepower, drivetrain, price cited from ingested doc
POST http://localhost:8080/vehicles/tesla-model3-2025-long-range/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What is the horsepower, drivetrain, and starting price?",
  "topK": 3,
  "mode": "HYBRID"
}

### ── 5. Ask about Tesla features (VECTOR mode)
POST http://localhost:8080/vehicles/tesla-model3-2025-long-range/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What are the key features and safety systems?",
  "topK": 3,
  "mode": "VECTOR"
}

### ── 6. Ask about BMW performance (BM25 keyword mode)
POST http://localhost:8080/vehicles/bmw-m3-2025-competition/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What engine does the M3 Competition use?",
  "topK": 3,
  "mode": "BM25"
}

###

### ── 7. Ask something NOT in the ingested data — expect fallback
### Expected: "I don't know based on the ingested documents."
POST http://localhost:8080/vehicles/tesla-model3-2025-long-range/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What color options are available?",
  "topK": 3,
  "mode": "HYBRID"
}

###

### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### FLEET SEARCH  — POST /vehicles/ask
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### ── 8. Numeric filter — over 500 horsepower
### Expected: rank 1 = Rivian (835hp), rank 2 = Corvette (670hp), rank 3 = BMW M3 (503hp)
POST http://localhost:8080/vehicles/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "which vehicles have over 500 horsepower",
  "topK": 3
}

###

### ── 9. Numeric filter — cheapest vehicles (under $50,000)
### Expected: Tesla Model 3 ($47,990), Toyota Camry ($33,400), Honda CR-V ($35,950)
POST http://localhost:8080/vehicles/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "vehicles under $50000",
  "topK": 3
}

###

### ── 10. Semantic search — best fuel economy
### Expected: Toyota Camry hybrid (51 MPG) and Honda CR-V hybrid near top
POST http://localhost:8080/vehicles/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "most fuel efficient vehicles best mpg",
  "topK": 3
}

###

### ── 11. Semantic search — electric vehicles
### Expected: Tesla Model 3, Rivian R1T
