### ── 20. Ingest validation — missing make (expect 400 / IllegalArgumentException)
POST http://localhost:8080/vehicles/ingest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": "test-bad-vehicle",
  "year": 2025,
  "make": "",
  "model": "Test",
  "trim": null
}

###

### ── 21. Ingest validation — vehicleId contains colon (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/vehicles/ingest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": "bad:id:vehicle",
  "year": 2025,
  "make": "Test",
  "model": "Car"
}

###

### ── 22. Fleet search — topK larger than ingested vehicles (should return all)
POST http://localhost:8080/vehicles/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "all vehicles",
  "topK": 20
}
